Do you like classic cars and quality @YouTube content? #QOTD 🤷🏻‍♂️
.
.
.
If you are anything like the three of us you probably enjoy spending your free time scouring the web for the best car content out there. While we respect and admire the work of fellow automotive Youtubers by the likes of @MrJWW, @VehicleVirgins, @Stradman we are always slightly disappointed by the lack of classic cars featured in their content. That brings us today’s clip taken from the @WeAreCurated Youtube channel called “Curated TV.” Enjoy this brief clip as John from Curated shows us this spectacular one owner, 2,500 Carrera GT and then head on over to their YouTube channel for more quality classic car content 😎
